name: Vita Silvia Shade
description:
The Silvia, with its 45 cm diameter and 45 cm height, is ideal in most places around the home. The blind-free design makes it perfect above a table, in a hall-way, the bedroom or indeed any place where you don't want to be blinded by a light bulb. And by mounting the Silvia on a lamp base it can even be used as a floor lamp. It comes in a sleek ultra-thin gift box, is made from indestructible polycarbonat and environmentally friendly polypropylene, and is designed to be put together at home in less than 15 minutes. 

Combine it with a standard E-27 socket and a max 60 watt light bulb, and the Silvia will soon be brightening up your home. Cord, socket and light source not included.

The Eos is a beautiful oval shape measures 45 cm in diameter and 30 cm in height. It's made from authentic bird feathers, each carefully positioned on a paper core by hand. It radiates a cosy and pleasant glow, and because the light bulb is shielded, the Eos is perfect to hang above a table, in a hall-way or indeed any place where you don't want to be blinded by a light source. Routine cleaning is easily done with a hairdryer and the Eos is simply mounted on virtually any socket within seconds and comes in beautiful gift box. 

Combine it with a standard E-27 socket and a max 30 watt light bulb. Cord, socket and light source not included.
